## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5ddf3-104">属性或字段必须是公共的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ddf3-104">The property or field must be public.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5ddf3-105">必须用特性标记包含属性的类 <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ddf3-105">The class that contains the property must be marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementEntityAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5ddf3-106">类中未用此或其他 WMI 提供程序扩展属性标记的任何字段或属性将不会进行检测。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ddf3-106">Any fields or properties in the class that are not marked with this or another WMI Provider Extensions attribute will not be instrumented.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="5ddf3-107">下面的示例演示如何使用 ManagementProbe 特性指示字段表示只读 WMI 属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ddf3-107">The following example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to indicate that a field represents a read-only WMI property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
[ManagementProbe]  
string count;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5ddf3-108">下一个示例演示如何使用 ManagementProbe 特性标记属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5ddf3-108">The next example shows how to use the ManagementProbe attribute to mark a property.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Use the ManagementProbe attribute to specify that a property  
// is a read-only property in the provider. Consumers will be  
// able to get this property value through WMI.  
[ManagementProbe]  
public int ReadOnlyProperty  
{  
    get { return this.propertyValue; }  
}  
```
